    About this item

    • Trouble for Less: Unlike other complicated manual releasing and locking operation, This gravity car phone holder only need to put your phone from the top, then it will slid into the the air vent mount smoothly and lock automatically and tightly using its 6 feet by gravity, meanwhile you can also charge your phone, truly free your hand and help you concentrate on driving.
    • Durable and Flexibility: Premium PC+ABS texture and aluminum alloy frame better for keeping the quality high and stable, even after 3,000 times tests, this UGREEN car phone cradle still alive. The Adjustable hook with locking knob for eliminating falling risk, 360° rotation for customized view and anti-scratch soft silicone pads for protecting your device, all make this cell phone holder a thoughtful keeper.
    • Universal Compatibility: This Automatic Locking phone holder can not only apply to all vertical and horizontal vent, but will not block the air flow. It fits all phones from 4.7 to Max 7 inches. It's compatible with iPhone 12 Pro Max 11 8 Plus, Samsung Galaxy S20 Note 10 S10, Google Pixel and more.
    • Fashion and Stylish: The combination of mirror and plastic make the texture comfortable, match of black and gray makes the appearance brightness, slid tray on the grips and curve edge make the product seem more unified.
    • Special Product for Special You: With our dedicated team we are always focusing on make the product convenient, innovative and premium. We simplified 2 even more steps operation, flimsy structure and so on, just for you.

    Product Description

    UGREEN Air Vent Phone Holder -- Your Safety, We care; Your Concern, We Require

    WHY UGREEN AIR VENT PHONE MOUNT?

    • Heart to Heart Process

    Adjust and lock with a rotary knob, adapting to air vent blades of different thickness and width; Experienced craftsman and advanced mould control the accuracy very carefully.

    • Premium and Preference

    High-temperature resistant PC+ABS and aluminium alloy material, 3,000 times fatigue tests, -22°F to -176°F test temperature, just to present a long-lived UGREEN cell phone holder.

    • Unit of Quality and Aesthetics

    In the history, good quality always means cumbersome, while aesthetics always means fragile, but UGREEN air vent phone holder features a solid multi-points construction and take harmony and elegant appearance into account, and its semi-polished mirror surface make it perfectly blend into your car interior.

    Read more

    • Stronger and More Stable

    Based on the top-classed materials and tests, this gravity car phone cradle is not easy to deform even after long-term use. With 6 grips feet, triangular support and anti-falling design, it can protect your phone from all round, even in bump road this phone cradle is much steadier than the dual-sized clips on the market.

    • View Friendly

    The arm of the mount is good for shortsightedness and farsightedness, you can adjust the length as you wish, the 360° joint ball can assist the hook holder easily to fit most vents, so that you can have the most proper view on sight, no need to draw your attention away from driving, ensure your safety in the biggest degree.

    • Kindly Note:

    1. The vent clip is only suitable for vertical or horizontal air vent blades, not for non-intensive, arc-shaped, or retraction type air vents.

    2. This cell phone holder can only work with phones case without exceeding 11mm thick.

    • Package Content:

    UGREEN gravity air vent phone mount x1
